Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:44.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,およそ遠しとされしもの　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.90,0:01:47.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,下等で奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.03,0:01:52.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,見慣れた動植物とは　まるで違うと　おぼしきモノ達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.99,0:01:56.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それら異形の一群を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.81,0:01:59.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ヒトは古くから畏れを含み
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.33,0:02:02.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いつしか総じて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:04.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,「蟲」と呼んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.82,0:02:32.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何だ この匂いは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.58,0:02:37.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,濃い 果実酒のような
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:43.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,光酒？ こんな所に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:48.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いや 違うな 饐えたような匂いになった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:02:59.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,匂いの源に 何がいる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:05.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,こっちを 見ている
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.44,0:03:13.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,体が竦む 動けない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:18.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,よーし そのままだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.89,0:03:20.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:24.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何だ 人か
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:28.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まあいい 見逃してやる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:38.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,楽になった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:41.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何だ 今のは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:46.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,猟師？ いや　丸切り手ぶらだった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:50.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それに 甘い匂いが消えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:54.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あれは 一体…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:11.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なんか昨日は疲れたな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:16.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ちっと精の付くもん食うか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:27.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,干し肉はねえだな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:32.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いや ここんとこ 獲物はさっぱりでな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:38.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうかい 向こうにあんな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:41.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,止めとけな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.73,0:04:45.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あいつんとこの肉は 臭くて敵わんぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:55.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,確かに 少し腐ったような…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.01,0:04:57.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,新しいのはねえのか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:04:59.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,家になら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:02.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そっちを分けちゃもらえんか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:06.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いいよ ついてきて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.89,0:05:19.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,辰兄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:24.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,家ん中からも腐臭は
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:27.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,今朝狩ってきた獲物 分けてくれって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:31.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,構わねえが…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:35.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,一体誰だ？ 珍しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:41.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,腐臭に混ざって 甘い匂い
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:46.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,昨日 山で嗅いだあの匂いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.39,0:05:55.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やあ 旅の人かい 上がりなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:58.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どれでも好きなの持ってくといい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.28,0:06:02.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,昨日の晩 山で狩りを？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:06.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ 今朝捌いたばかりだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:11.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃ その肉はずっと日にでも晒してたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:15.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あんたも 家の獲物が臭えってのか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:19.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どこかだよ 全然匂わねぇじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:20.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なあ 卯介
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:22.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まぁ いいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:23.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃ 今から狩ってきてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.83,0:06:26.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そんなら 文句はねえだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:29.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何 半時もあれば済む
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:32.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そこで少し 待っててくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:53.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,こっちだ 来い
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.15,0:07:06.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうだ そのままだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:16.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,止せ　
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:19.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あんた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:20.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もういい　
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:25.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前さんの狩った獲物は どんなに新しくとも 不味いはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:28.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どういうことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:30.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,意のままに獲物を狩る手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.12,0:07:35.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,血筋に 同じ手を持つ者はないか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:38.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ 親父もそうだったが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:43.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,掌に 眼玉のような痣があるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:48.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そいつは 腐酒というものに冒されてる印だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:54.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,腐酒というのは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:07:59.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,生命の素たるもの 光酒の腐れてしまったものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:03.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,本来 成るはずの蟲と成れず
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:07.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,赤い泥状となり 地下水から地上に湧き出る
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:12.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,果実酒のような匂いがするが 毒性があり
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:15.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,高い濃度で口にすれば 死に至る
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:21.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だが 極稀に 毒に耐える体質の者がある
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.95,0:08:24.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,腐酒単体には意思もなく
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:27.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ただ 更なる腐敗を待つだけのものだが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:33.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,動物の体内に入り 血に紛れると 命を得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:36.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,宿主もまた 特殊な力を得る
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:43.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,甘い匂いを掌から出し 獲物を引き付け 酔わせ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:44.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,容易く狩りをする
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:48.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そして それは血を介して
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:51.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,子々孫々まで伝わってゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:56.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,へえ そういうもんだったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:09:00.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ただ 力を得る者は極僅かだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:02.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,力を得なかった者は
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:05.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,毒のため長くは生きられない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:07.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ばあちゃんは 血を吐いて死んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.70,0:09:10.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,弟も同じ病だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:13.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それもその腐酒ってやつのせいなのか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.54,0:09:16.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,治してやる方法はないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:19.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,このままじゃ 卯介も
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:22.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,安心しろ 治療法ならある
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:26.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,光酒を一定量飲めば 腐酒は消滅する
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:28.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,今は手持ちが足りねえが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:29.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,調達してこよう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:33.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうか よかったな 卯介
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:36.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,これでもう 苦しい思いをしねえで済むぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:39.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:43.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,治療が必要なのは 弟だけじゃねえぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:46.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺？ 俺は何ともねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:50.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前さんの父親 最後はどうなった？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:57.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,知ってるなら話は早い 早めに手を打ったほうがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:10:00.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そんな特別な力などなくとも
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:02.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そんだけ立派な体がありゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:05.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟で食ってくだけの狩りはできるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:09.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:11.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それじゃ二人分な
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.14,0:10:14.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,一月程度で持ってこれると思う
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,よろしく頼むよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:20.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,それまでまた 間違って人を狩ろうとするなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:25.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,もしかして 昨夜会ったの　あんただったか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:28.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そりゃ悪かったな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:32.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,いつも日が落ちてから狩りをするのか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:36.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ 獣は夜歩き回るやつが多い
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.37,0:10:40.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,昼間多いのは 夜目の利かねえ鳥くらいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:43.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥など狩っても つまらない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:48.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なら 提灯くらい持ってくれ 紛らわしいし 不用心だろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:51.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,火があっちゃ 獣が寄り付かねぇよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:55.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,この山なら 目をつぶってても歩けるし
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:57.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺を襲う獣もいねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.73,0:11:00.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,月の光で十分なんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:06.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前は 山の王にでもなったつもりか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.53,0:11:09.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前も山の一部にすぎんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:14.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何で命を落とすかなど 誰にも知れんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.93,0:11:20.69,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,たとえ それが山で最も恐れられる 獣だとしてもな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:25.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ 肝に銘じとくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.06,0:11:32.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,辰兄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:36.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ちゃんと 薬飲んでくれるよね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.52,0:11:41.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺 元の辰兄に戻って欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:47.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何言ってんだ 俺は別に何も変わらんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:34.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ギンコさん 薬は？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.11,0:12:38.39,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ 手に入れた 兄貴は？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:40.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,狩りだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:44.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,相変わらずだな こんな宵の口に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:46.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ギンコさん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:50.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,一緒に来て 早く辰兄に 薬あげて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:08.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,これは… みんな辰がやったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:15.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父ちゃんがいなくなってから 辰兄は父ちゃんに似てきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:21.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父ちゃんも よくこんな余分な狩りをしてた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:33.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そら 持って帰って捌いとけ　
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:37.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父ちゃん まだ家にいっぱいあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:39.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なら売ってこい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:42.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,みんな 臭くて要らないって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.43,0:13:45.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なら そこらに捨てておけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:50.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,辰兄 父ちゃんなんでこんなことするのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:56.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父ちゃんは 生きてるものを狩ること自体が好きなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:13:58.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父ちゃんに逆らうな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.16,0:14:01.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺らも いつ狩られっか分かんねぇぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.49,0:14:06.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,危ねえと思ったら 母ちゃんみてえに逃げるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:09.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,怖かねえよ 俺にだって力はあんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:12.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前は俺が守ってやっから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:14.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:21.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父ちゃんの異変が始まったのは そんなある日だった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:24.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,辰兄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:25.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:27.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父ちゃん変だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:32.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,体の向こうが 透けて見える
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:46.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父ちゃん 影がない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.14,0:14:50.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,そして あの日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:53.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父ちゃん 朝飯だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:14:56.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父ちゃん？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:02.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父ちゃんは 消えてなくなってしまってた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:12.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,自分より強い先代がいなくなると
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:16.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,枷が外れたように  その子孫の力が増すという
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:19.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,腐酒の侵食が進み
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:23.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やがて 体を完全に乗っ取られる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.39,0:15:28.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,つまり 完全に蟲の側に行っちまうんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.35,0:15:30.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,父親は死んだわけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.02,0:15:34.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,実体をなくし 心もなくして
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:37.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,今も 山を彷徨っているはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:42.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,辰兄も このままじゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:48.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,甘い…匂い
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.58,0:15:56.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,やあ 戻ったのかい ギンコさん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.03,0:16:00.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ 光酒は手に入れた 早く飲め
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.47,0:16:05.57,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,卯介に 飲ませといてくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:10.68,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺は また気が向いた時にするよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:16.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,山に君臨する気分ってのは ずいぶんといいもんらしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:18.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だが目を覚ませ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:23.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前は 意思すら持たねえ蟲に踊らされてるだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:27.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,うるせえな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:31.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,あんた 自分の立場分かってんのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:35.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,卯介の薬だけ置いてってやってくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:40.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺はなぁ もう二度と御免なんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.76,0:16:47.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,親父がいた頃みてえに 狩られるかもしれねえ側に戻るなんてな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:49.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,辰兄 止めてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:52.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,大丈夫だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.71,0:16:56.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,怖いことなんてないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:59.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺 襲われない方法知ってから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:01.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だから…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:06.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,辰兄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:11.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,辰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:15.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,どこへ行った
