Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.93,0:17:32.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,元の俺に戻ってやらねえと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,卯介？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:50.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まさか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:54.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,何を撃った
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:17:59.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,熊だと思うが 崖から落ちちまった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:07.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,腐酒だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:18.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,くそ 腕が動かねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:23.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,このままじゃ 獣にやられちまう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.18,0:18:28.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ここで 朝まで待つか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:02.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,夜がこんなに 長いとは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:11.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,闇がこんなに 恐ろしいとは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.26,0:19:31.59,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,辰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:33.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,辰兄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.24,0:19:36.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ここだ 卯介
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:41.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,辰兄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:51.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,まずい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:52.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,待て 出てくるな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:25.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,鳥どもは なんで 俺の腕を…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.21,0:20:32.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,動物 中でも特に鳥類は 目玉文様に恐れを抱く
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:35.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,果実の匂いに引き寄せられても
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.53,0:20:40.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,これまで掌の文様のために 襲えずにいたのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:44.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,目玉が血で隠れた時
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.53,0:20:48.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,その腕は 鳥にとって甘美な餌となったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:53.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,鳥の餌か
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.63,0:20:57.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,辰兄 だいぶ熱下がったね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:21:02.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,お前 ずいぶん顔色よくなったな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.73,0:21:04.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,だろう もうずっと血を吐かない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:07.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,きっと 光酒ってのが効いたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:10.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,俺も狩り覚えるからさ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:14.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,辰兄も 早く元気になって 一緒にしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.90,0:21:25.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.29,0:21:40.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0000,0000,0000,,なんだよ 嚇かすない
